Title: Walk the Solar System
Book Description: Stretched down a long hall of the hotel is a scale-model of the solar system! At the position of the Sun and orbits of the planets- you will find a poster(with a QR code) with more information on that body.

Title: MegOperation
Book Description: Don't touch the sides! Come play Lansing Maker Network's MegOperation-  an eye-catching- interactive- large-scale version of of the classic game Operation.
